          <span class="faded">shape resilient systems, and build + lead inspired engineering teams.</span>
        </h1>
      </div>
      <div class="balcom-hero-image-wrapper animate-right delay-200">
        <Image 
          src={me} 
          alt="Reynaldi Wong" 
          class="balcom-avatar"
          width={400}
          height={500}
        />
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Bio / Philosophy -->
    <section class="balcom-bio-split">
      <div class="balcom-bio-left animate-left delay-300">
        <!-- Empty or small intro text if needed -->
      </div>
      <div class="balcom-bio-right animate-right delay-300">
        <div class="balcom-intro">
          <p>
            Currently, I‚Äôm a DevOps Engineer at <strong>Digital Daya Teknologi</strong>,
            empowering development teams to deploy faster, safer, and with greater confidence.
          </p>
          <p class="balcom-links">
            <a href="mailto:contact@reynaldi.dev">Email me</a>, 
            or shout over on <a href="https://linkedin.com" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a> 
            or <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank">GitHub</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <h2 class="balcom-subheading animate-left delay-400" style="margin-bottom: 4rem; max-width: 800px;">
      Over 3 years bridging development and operations into delightful developer experiences.
    </h2>

    <!-- Experience List -->
    <section class="balcom-experience-section animate-right delay-400">
      
      <div class="balcom-experience-item">
        <div class="balcom-year">2023 ‚Äî Present</div>
        <div class="balcom-timeline-dot"></div>
        <div class="balcom-details">
          <h3>DevOps Engineer at [Digital Daya Teknologi]</h3>
          <p>Maintained and developed cloud infrastructure and CI/CD pipelines for applications at Nobu Bank.</p>
          <div class="balcom-bottom-line">
            Bottom Line ‚Üí Reduced deployment time by 40% and improved system reliability.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="balcom-experience-item">
        <div class="balcom-year">2021 ‚Äî 2023</div>
        <div class="balcom-timeline-dot"></div>
        <div class="balcom-details">
          <h3>Project Supervisor at Dankos Farma</h3>
          <p>Designed and provisioned on-premise infrastructure, including servers and networking, for data center.</p>
          <div class="balcom-bottom-line">
            Bottom Line ‚Üí Successfully migrated legacy systems to virtualized environments.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="balcom-experience-item">
        <div class="balcom-year">2019 ‚Äî 2021</div>
        <div class="balcom-timeline-dot"></div>
        <div class="balcom-details">
          <h3>Automation Specialist at Finusolprima</h3>
          <p>Implemented automated control systems for manufacturing lines to improve efficiency.</p>
          <div class="balcom-bottom-line">
             Bottom Line ‚Üí Increased production output by 15% through automation.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </section>

    <!-- This & That / Tools -->
    <h2 class="balcom-subheading animate-left delay-500" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">This & That.</h2>
    <div class="balcom-grid-split">
      <div class="animate-left delay-500">
        <p style="color: var(--secondary-text);">
          A lazy person on the hunt for efficiency. Long-suffering <u>Kubernetes fan</u>, avid automation collector, average gamer, and aspiring <u>home chef</u>.
          <br/><br/>
          Based in <u>Jakarta</u>.
          <br/><br/>
          Been a DevOps Engineer for <ExperienceTimer client:only="preact" startDate="2022-08-01" />.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="animate-right delay-500">
        <!-- Lightning Round equivalent or Tools -->
         <p style="font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Lightning Round ‚ö°</p>
         <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; color: var(--secondary-text); line-height: 2;">
           <li>‚òï Coffee over Tea</li>
           <li>üêß Linux over Windows</li>
           <li>‚ö° VS Code over Vim (sorry!)</li>
           <li>üéµ Rock over Pop</li>
         </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Tools Link -->
    <a href="/tools" class="balcom-tools-link animate-left delay-600">
      <div style="display: flex; align-items: baseline; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <span class="balcom-tools-title">Tools</span>
        <span class="balcom-tools-desc">DNS Lookup, SSL Checker, JSON Formatter</span>
      </div>
      <span class="balcom-tools-arrow">‚Üí</span>
    </a>

  </div>

  <script>
    const observerOptions = {
      root: null,
      rootMargin: '0px',
      threshold: 0.1
    };

    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries, observer) => {
      entries.forEach(entry => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add('in-view');
          observer.unobserve(entry.target);
        }
      });
    }, observerOptions);

    const animatedElements = document.querySelectorAll('.animate-left, .animate-right, .animate-load');
    animatedElements.forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
  </script>
</BaseLayout>
